tric%20on%20its%20own%20to%20determine%20a%20brand's%20overall%20worth.%20Quantifiable%20brand%20trust%20and%20loyalty%20have%20been%20kicked%20around%20as%20more%20modernized%20ways%20to%20assess%20a%20brand's%20valuation%2C%20particularly%20as%20loyalty%20dissipated%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20usurped%20by%20convenience.%20Meanwhile%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20acquisition%20continues%20to%20rise%2C%20retention%20is%20a%20new%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloping%20the%20means%20to%20quantify%20a%20brand's%20true%20value%20is%20the%20most%20important%20part%20of%20a%20marketing%20organization%20that%20needs%20to%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20new%20disruptive%20thinking%20on%20brand%20value%20deserves%20consideration%20%E2%80%94%20the%20power%20of%20emotion.%20While%20we%20all%20know%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20customers%20behave%20or%20act%2C%20we%20know%20little%20about%20how%20they%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20power%20of%20emotion%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Equinox%20example%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmotion%20is%20the%20new%20currency%20driving%20quantifiable%20brand%20growth.%20So%2C%20what%20is%20emotion%20exactly%3F%20It's%20often%20defined%20as%20instinctive%20or%20intuitive%20feeling%20as%20distinguished%20from%20reasoning%20or%20knowledge.%20Conventional%20wisdom%20holds%20that%20thought%20precedes%20emotion%20but%20in%20fact%2C%20science%20has%20consistently%20proven%20that%20emotion%20precedes%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImagine%20if%20you%20could%20take%20this%20thinking%20even%20further%20to%20precisely%20score%20how%20trusting%20of%20and%20loyal%20your%20customers%20are%20to%20your%20brand%20to%20get%20to%20a%20precise%20total%20valuation%2C%20that%20is%20inarguable%2C%20no%20different%20than%20the%20accuracy%20of%20a%20stock's%20price.%20One%20can%20debate%20if%20a%20stock%20should%20trade%20higher%20or%20lower%2C%20but%20what%20it%20trades%20at%20on%20a%20given%20day%20based%20on%20how%20the%20markets%20are%20performing%20is%20an%20uncontested%20benchm