tions.%20First%2C%20consider%20shopping%20with%20more%20budget-friendly%20retailers%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa-couch%23wayfair-1%5C%22%3EWayfair%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sofa-couch%23zinus-4%5C%22%3EZinus%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20can%20also%20wait%20for%20sales%2C%20which%20typically%20occur%20during%20the%20summertime%20and%20during%20major%20sale%20events%20like%20Black%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20great%20way%20to%20save%20money%20while%20shopping%20is%20to%20find%20out%20if%20any%20of%20the%20brands%20you're%20interested%20in%20have%20a%20retail%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20do%20a%20little%20research%20and%20possibly%20a%20minor%20repair%20here%20and%20there%2C%20you%20can%20score%20a%20quality%20sofa%20for%2030%25%20less%20than%20the%20MSRP%20by%20locating%20the%20retail%20outlets%20of%20some%20of%20your%20favorite%20manufacturers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Li.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20recommend%2C%20if%20you%20can%2C%20spending%20more%20money%20initially%20to%20ensure%20you'll%20purchase%20a%20piece%20that%20will%20last%20you%20a%20long%20time%20versus%20having%20to%20constantly%20replace%20cheaper-made%20furniture%20every%20few%20years.%20Another%20tip%20is%20to%20buy%20modular%20furniture%20(Burrow%20is%20a%20popular%20option)%20that%20can%20be%20added%20on%20to%20and%20adjusted%20over%20time%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20slowly%20expand%20your%20seating%20as%20your%20budget%20increases.%20You%20can%20also%20purchase%20a%20smaller%20sofa%20with%20a%20chaise%2C%20which%20will%20allow%20for%20additional%20seating%20space%20at%20a%20lower%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EShould%20I%20purchase%20a%20pre-made%20or%20custom%20couch%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20deciding%20whether%20to%20purchase%20a%20pre-made%20or%20custom%20couch%2C%20you%20should%20consider%20two%20main%20factors%3A%20budget%20