20areas%20that%20are%20BJP%20strongholds.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20party%20won%2072%20of%20the%2093%20seats%20going%20to%20polls%20today%2C%2026%20of%20them%20in%20Gujarat%20alone.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20other%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20had%20done%20extremely%20well%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20could%20be%20a%20dark%20horse%20given%20the%20massive%20sex%20scandal%20that%20has%20hit%20BJP%20ally%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular.%20The%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20scandal%2C%20but%20it%20is%20anybody's%20guess%20which%20way%20the%20women%20voters%20would%20lean.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaharashtra%2C%20where%2011%20of%2048%20seats%20are%20going%20to%20polls%2C%20has%20proved%20harder%20to%20read%20given%20the%20seismic%20political%20shifts%20the%20state%20has%20seen%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20The%20key%20battles%20will%20be%20Pawar%20versus%20Pawar%20--%20with%20the%20factions%20led%20by%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%20trying%20to%20establish%20dominance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20states%20going%20to%20polls%20in%20phase%203%20include%20Assam%20(4%20seats)%2C%20Bihar%20(5)%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20(7)%2C%20Goa%20(2)%2C%20Gujarat%20(26)%2C%20Karnataka%20(14)%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20(8)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(11)%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(10)%2C%20West%20Bengal%20(4)%2C%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20(2).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPolling%20will%20also%20take%20place%20in%20Betul%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20election%20due%20on%20Phase%202%20was%20postponed%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20candidate%20from%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EElection%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20constituency%20was%20postponed%20after%20the%20BJP%20flagged%20concern%20about%20the%20weather%2C%20which%20was%20forcing%20shut%20a%20tunnel%20connecting%20the%20two%20ends%20of%20the%20constituency.%20It%20was%20proving%20a%20huge%20hurdle%20in%20campaigning%2C%20said%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20not%20contesting%20from%20the%20seat.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKey%20candidates%20for%20this%20phase%20includes%20Union%20ministers%20Amit%20Shah%20from%20Gujarat's%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20from%20Guna%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20from%20Karnataka's%20Dharwad%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20from%20Vidisha%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20key%20Opposition%20members%20in%20fray%20include%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Dimple%20Yadav%20from%20Mainpuri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3B%20Congress's%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20from%C2%A0%20Berhampore%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20from%20Rajgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3B%20NCP's%20Supriya%20Sule%20from%20Maharashtra's%20Baramati.%20Perfume%20baron%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%20of%20AIDUF%20is%20contesting%20from%20Assam's%20Dhubri.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20next%20phase%20of%20election%20is%20due%20on%20May%2013.%20The%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20be%20held%20on%20June%204%20after%20the%20last%20phase%20of%20the%20election%20ends%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715021700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcnt8g7vo_voting-lok-sabha-polls_625x300_25_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-phase-3-many-bjp-strongholds-up-for-poll-10-points-5604206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Election%20on%2093%20constituencies%20across%2010%20states%20and%202%20Union%20Territories%20will%20be%20held%20today%20as%20the%20third%20of%20the%20mammoth%20seven-phase%20election%20rolled%20around.%20Election%20on%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20constituency%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20postponed%20to%20May%2025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-phase-3-many-bjp-strongholds-up-for-poll-10-points-5604206%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2