n%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECondition%201%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20the%20Hardik%20Pandya-led%20side%20has%20to%20win%20all%20of%20its%20remaining%20two%20matches%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20league%20campaign.%20MI%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20on%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECondition%202%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHope%20that%20no%20other%20team%20crosses%20the%2012-point%20mark%20in%20IPL%202024%20standings.%20At%20present%2C%20SRH%2C%20LSG%20and%20CSK%20already%20have%2012%20points%20to%20their%20name.%20Hence%2C%20at%20least%20two%20of%20these%20franchises%20will%20have%20to%20lose%20their%20remaining%20matches%20in%20the%20league%20campaign.%20With%20KKR%20and%20RR%20already%20sitting%20at%20the%20No.%201%20and%20No.%202%20spots%20respectively%20with%2016%20points%20each%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20to%20topple%20them.%20In%20fact%2C%20big%20wins%20against%20other%20teams%20for%20KKR%20and%20RR%20would%20only%20benefit%20MI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECondition%203%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMumbai%20Indians%20have%20a%20Net%20Run%20Rate%20of%20-0.212%20at%20present.%20Even%20if%20MI%20win%20all%20of%20their%20remaining%20matches%2C%20they%20will%20need%20to%20do%20that%20by%20big%20margins%20in%20order%20to%20get%20into%20a%20positive%20NRR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20that%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20if%20the%20NRR%20of%20other%20teams%20at%2012%20points%20is%20better%20than%20MI.%20Though%20you%20never%20say%20never%20in%20a%20sport%20like%20cricket%2C%20it's%20fair%20to%20assert%20that%20Mumbai%20Indians'%20chances%20of%20IPL%202024%20playoffs%20qualification%20don't%20instill%20much%20hope%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20their%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715020620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F035absgg_s_625x300_06_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fipl-2024-points-table-how-win-over-sunrisers-hyderabad-is-crucial-for-mumbai-indians-playoff-dreams-5603999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%20kept%20their%20IPL%202024%20playoff%20dreams%20alive%20with%20a%20crucial%20victory%20over%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Third%20Phase%20Of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%20Today%2C%20BJP%20Defends%20Big%20Score%20From%202019%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20phase%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20begins%20this%20morning%20with%20voting%20for%2093%20seats%20across%2012%20states%20and%20union%20territories%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20belt%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%20Assam%2C%20Bengal%2C%20Goa%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20the%20UTs%20of%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20and%20Diu%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20complete%20the%20list%20for%20this%20phase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20has%20been%20called%20off%20in%20south%20Gujarat's%20Surat%20after%20the%20Congress'%20pick%2C%20Nilesh%20Kumbhani%2C%20was%20rejected%20over%20alleged%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20signatures%20of%20proposers.%20Mr%20Kumbhani%20later%20went%20missing%20for%20a%20while%20amid%20rumours%20he%20was%20set%20to%20join%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20Mukesh%20Dalal%20was%20declared%20elected%20by%20default%20-%20amid%20a%20still-simmering%20storm%20-%20after%20eight%20other%20candidates%2C%20including%20seven%20independents%2C%20withdrew%20from%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurat%2C%20therefore%2C%20became%20the%20first%20seat%20to%20be%20declared%20(and%20won%20by%20the%20BJP)%20in%20this%20election.%20Since%20then%2C%20similar%20drama%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Indore%20has%20made%20it%20BJP%202%20-%200%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2093%20seats%20in%20this%20phase%20for%20which%20opposition%20candidates%20remain%2C%2025%20(not%20including%20Surat)%20are%20from%20Gujarat.%20The%20BJP%20won%20all%2026%20in%202019.%2014%20of%20Karnataka's%2028%20seats%20will%20vote%20in%20this%20phase%20and%20the%20BJP%20also%20won%20all%20of%20them%2C%20as%20it%20did%20the%20nine%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%2029%20seats%20that%20vote%20today.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20won%20a%20staggering%2080%20of%20these%2093%20seats%20last%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERetaining%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20these%20seats%20will%20be%20key%20for%20the%20BJP's%20'abki%20baar%2C%20400%20paar'%20goal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20won%20only%2011%20of%20these%20seats%20last%20time%2C%20with%20the%20other%20two%20-%20Assam%20and%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20-%20electing%20independent%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20big%20names%20standing%20in%20this%20phase%20are%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20(Civil%20Aviation)%20and%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20(Parliamentary%20Affairs)%2C%20and%20Purushottam%20Rupala%2C%20who%20is%20the%20junior%20Dairy%20and%20Fisheries%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20will%20defend%20his%20Gandhinagar%20seat%20in%20Gujarat.%20The%20seat%20was%20the%20bastion%20of%20former%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20LK%20Advani%2C%20who%20held%20it%20from%201998%20till%202019.%20The%20Congress%20hasn't%20won%20the%20Gujarat%20capital%20since%20GI%20Patel's%20win%20way%20back%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia%20will%20look%20to%20win%20back%20(and%20defend)%20his%20family%20stronghold%20of%20Guna%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20He%20held%20the%20seat%20for%2012%20years%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20but%20lost%20it%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Krishna%20Pal%20Yadav%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20a%20year%20before%20he%20jumped%20ship%20to%20the%20saffron%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%20will%20look%20to%20win%20his%20Dharwad%20seat%20in%20Karnataka%20for%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20time.%20The%2014%20Karnataka%20seats%20voting%20today%20are%20from%20the%20BJP's%20strongholds%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20the%20southern%20state.%20Two%20other%20significant%20seats%20from%20these%2014%20are%20Shimoga%20and%20Haveri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShimoga%20is%20the%20family%20turf%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20BS%20Yedyiyurappa.%20The%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20his%20son%20and%20sitting%20MP%20BY%20Raghavendra%2C%20which%20upset%20senior%20leader%20KS%20Eshwarappa%2C%20who%20will%20contest%20as%20an%20independent%20after%20being%20expelled%20from%20the%20party.%20The%20other%20seat%20-%20Haveri%20-%20will%20see%20another%20former%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20-%20Basavaraj%20Bommai%20-%20contesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rupala%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20contesting%20the%20Rajkot%20seat%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20another%20BJP%20bastion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20-%20who%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20having%20engineered%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20the%20November%20state%20election%20but%20was%20passed%20over%20for%20another%20term%20in%20the%20top%20post%20-%20is%20also%20contesting.%20He%20stands%20from%20his%20family%20seat%20of%20Vidisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20opposition's%20ranks%2C%20another%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20will%20contest%20the%20Rajgarh%20seat.%20This%20was%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20past%20two%20elections%2C%20but%20Mr%20Singh%20won%20this%20seat%20twice%20before%20that%20-%20in%201984%20and%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20-%20Sharadchandra%20Pawar%20leader%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20who%20is%20party%20patriarch%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%20-%20will%20stand%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Baramati%20seat%2C%20which%20voted%20for%20her%20father%20six%20times%20previously%20and%20made%20her%20an%20MP%20in%202009%2C%202014%2C%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20headline%20here%20is%20Ms%20Sule's%20contest%20against%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20Mr%20Pawar%20-%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20nephew%20and%20Supriya%20Sule's%20cousin%20-%20led%20a%20rebellion%20within%20the%20formerly%20undivided%20NCP%2C%20siding%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20triggering%20a%20messy%20split.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20continuing%20battle%20to%20go%20one-up%20on%20his%20uncle%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20has%20his%20eye%20set%20on%20Baramati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20desperate%20to%20win%20too%3B%20victory%20here%20will%20be%20a%20statement%20of%20intent%20against%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%2C%20of%20which%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction%20is%20a%20part.%20It%20will%20also%20boost%20the%20'mission%2045'%20goal%2C%20which%20is%20to%20win%2045%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2010%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20seats%20polling%20in%20this%20round%2C%20one%20is%20Mainpuri%2C%20which%20is%20a%20family%20stronghold%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20boss%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20Mr%20Yadav's%20wife%2C%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20is%20the%20sitting%20MP%20after%20winning%20a%202022%20bypoll%20due%20to%20the%20death%20of%20SP%20patriarch%20Mulayam%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20phase%20is%20a%20key%20one%20for%20the%20Yadav%20family%2C%20with%20Akshay%20Yadav%20(Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20cousin)%20and%20Aditya%20Yadav%20(Shivpal%20Yadav's%20son)%20contesting%20Firozabad%20and%20Budaun%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMainpuri%20isn't%20the%20only%20big%20seat%20from%20UP%20in%20this%20phase%3B%20Hathras%2C%20a%20reserved%20seat%20in%20an%20area%20that%20has%20seen%20shocking%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20and%20Agra%20are%20also%20voting.%20Both%20are%20BJP%20strongholds.%20Fatehpur%20Sikri%20-%20a%20BJP%20seat%20since%202009%20-%20is%20also%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEleven%20of%20Maharashtra's%2048%20seats%20-%20the%20most%20of%20any%20state%20after%20UP's%2080%20-%20vote%20today%2C%20including%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Baramati.%20The%20other%2010%20include%20the%20reserved%20seats%20of%20Latur%20and%20Solapur%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Sangli%20and%20Kolhapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHigh-profile%20seats%20from%20other%20states%20include%20Murshidabad%20and%20Jangipur%20from%20Bengal%2C%20both%20of%20which%20were%20won%20by%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool.%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party%20is%2C%20on%20paper%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20but%20it%20is%20contesting%20all%2042%20seats%20against%20both%20its%20allies%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20steadily%20gaining%20ground%20in%20the%20eastern%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Bengal%2C%20Maldaha%20Uttar%20and%20Dakshin%20are%20also%20voting%20today.%20These%20are%20held%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress.%20The%20latter%20was%20only%20of%20two%20seats%20the%20Congress%20won%20in%20the%202019%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%20-%20which%20was%20swept%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20the%20ruling%20JDU%20and%20the%20LJP%2C%20in%20the%20last%20election%20-%20there%20are%20five%20seats%20voting.%20All%20five%20were%20claimed%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh's%20seven%20remaining%20seats%20also%20vote%20today%2C%20as%20do%20both%20South%20and%20North%20Goa%20(the%20BJP's%20Pallavi%20Dempo%20stands%20from%20the%20former)%20and%20the%20lone%20seat%20from%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20four%20phases%20of%20the%20general%20election%20to%20come%2C%20with%20the%20fourth%20on%20May%2013%2C%20fifth%20on%20May%2020%2C%20sixth%20on%20May%2025%2C%20an