a-discusses-her-terrible-experiences-with-toxic-co-stars-and-female-producers-they-pretend-to-be-feminists%2Farticleshow%2F109893960.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mass%20Resignation%20Hits%20National%20Conference%20Over%20INDIA%20Bloc's%20Ladakh%20Pick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20leaders%20of%20the%20party's%20Kargil%20unit%20resigned%20en%20masse%20in%20Ladakh%20today%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20INDIA%20block%20candidate%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20leaders%20submitted%20their%20resignations%20to%20party%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20after%20they%20were%20allegedly%20pressured%20by%20the%20party's%20high%20command%20to%20support%20the%20Congress's%20candidate%20Tsering%20Namgyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mass%20resignation%20came%20hours%20after%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20warned%20party%20leaders%20in%20Kargil%20of%20disciplinary%20action%20if%20they%20failed%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20party's%20decision%20to%20support%20INDIA%20block%20candidate%20Tsering%20Namgyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNC%20President%20Dr%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20has%20directed%20the%20Kargil%20unit%20of%20the%20party%20to%20support%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20candidate%20-%20T%20Namgyal%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20for%20the%20Ladakh%20seat.%20He%20has%20told%20his%20colleagues%20that%20failure%20to%20follow%20this%20directive%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20serious%20breach%20of%20party%20discipline%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20in%20Kargil%20have%20already%20raised%20a%20banner%20of%20revolt%20against%20the%20party%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebel%20leaders%20of%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20Congress%20have%20fielded%20a%20candidate%20backed%20by%20all%20the%20religious%20and%20social%20groups%20of%20Kargil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20controversy%20is%20an%20old%20political%2