Revanna%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20of%20allowing%20the%20JD(S)%20MP%20to%20go%20out%20of%20the%20country%20and%20releasing%20the%20incriminating%20sex%20videos%20after%20the%20polls%20were%20over%20in%20the%20region%20dominated%20by%20Vokkaligas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesnownews.com%2Felections%2Fpm-modi-unfiltered-on-prajwal-revanna-sex-tape-scandal-stay-tuned-for-exclusive-interview-at-9-pm-article-109882622%5C%22%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20responsibility%20to%20take%20action%20in%20the%20raging%20matter%20lay%20with%20the%20state%20government%20as%20it%20was%20a%20law%20and%20order%20issue%2C%20according%20to%20the%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview%20provided%20by%20the%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20presence%20of%20thousands%20of%20videos%20implies%20that%20it%20is%20of%20the%20time%20when%20the%20JD(S)%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress.%20These%20videos%20were%20gathered%20when%20they%20were%20in%20power%20and%20they%20released%20it%20during%20the%20elections%20after%20Vokkaligas%20exercised%20their%20franchise%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20were%20released%20after%20he%20was%20sent%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%2C%20calling%20the%20development%20very%20suspicious.%20If%20the%20state%20government%20had%20information%2C%20it%20should%20have%20kept%20a%20watch%20and%20there%20should%20have%20been%20vigil%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20did%20not%20do%20anything%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20was%20not%20informed.%20This%20means%20that%20it%20was%20a%20political%20game%20and%20they%20know%20that%20these%20videos%20were%20from%20the%20time%20they%20were%20in%20alliance%20and%20they%20accumulated%20these%20videos.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20my%20issue%2C%20my%20issue%20is%20that%20any%20culprit%20should%20not%20be%20spared.%20These%20games%20should%20be%20stopped%20in%20our%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20transcript.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20Modi%20is%20concerned%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20BJP%20is%20concerned%2C%20as%20far%20as%20our%20Constitution%20is%20concerned%2C%20I%20am%20of%20the%20clear%20view%20that%20there%20should%20be%20zero%20tolerance%20against%20such%20people.%20Stringent%20punishment%20should%20be%20given%20using%20all%20the%20legal%20options%20available.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20bring%20him%20back%20and%20strict%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20him.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20ifs%20and%20buts.%26quot%3B%20The%20Congress%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20ran%20an%20alliance%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20after%20the%202018%20polls%20and%20parted%20ways%20after%20fighting%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20prime%20minister%20H%20D%20Deve%20Gowda-led%20party%20entered%20into%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20September%20last%20year%20and%20they%20are%20fighting%20the%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20used%20the%20issue%20of%20Revanna's%20alleged%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20women%2C%20captured%20in%20nearly%203000%20video%20clips%2C%20to%20target%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevanna%2C%20Gowda's%20grandson%2C%20is%20again%20in%20the%20fray%20from%20Hassan%2C%20where%20polling%20was%20held%20on%20April%2026.%20The%20regional%20party%20enjoys%20influence%20in%20south%20Karnataka%2C%20especially%20among%20Vokkaligas%2C%20the%20community%20Gowda%20belongs%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20poser%20about%20his%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress%20over%20issues%20like%20inheritance%20tax%20and%20redistribution%20of%20wealth%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20he%20has%20cited%20the%20language%2C%20words%20and%20written%20assurance%20of%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leaders%20to%20make%20his%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20time%20I%20have%20exposed%20them%20to%20the%20hilt.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20are%20rattled.%20When%20they%20go%20seeking%20votes%20of%20one%20community%2C%20they%20speak%20differently%2C%20and%20when%20they%20approach%20the%20other%20community%2C%20they%20take%20a%20neutral%20stand.%20This%20is%20their%20duplicity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20unlike%20the%20BJP%20which%20always%20talked%20about%20building%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20continuously%20lying%20while%20attacking%20the%20BJP%20by%20alleging%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20some%20BJP%20members%20said%20something%20and%20the%20Congress%20blew%20it%20out%20of%20proportion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20refusing%20to%20hear%20our%20version.%20Now%2C%20the%20Congress%20asks%20where%20wealth%20distribution%20and%20inheritance%20tax%20are%20mentioned%20in%20its%20manifesto.%20The%20Congress%20shouldn't%20have%20double%20standards.%20The%20Congress%20will%20have%20to%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpanding%20his%20arguments%20against%20reservation%20based%20on%20religion%2C%20he%20said%20such%20an%20idea%20goes%20against%20the%20Constitution.%20Citing%20his%20government's%20welfare%20measures%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20he%20does%20not%20discriminate%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715012220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtv