rs%20began%20to%20recede%2C%20they%20left%20behind%20many%20challenges%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20chill%20in%20the%20air%20and%20the%20bacteria%20breeding%20in%20the%20murky%20waters%20had%20only%20added%20to%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20against%20tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TB)%20that%20the%20community%20was%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20often%20started%20with%20a%20cough%20and%20before%20the%20person%20knew%20it%2C%20they%20were%20detected%20with%20TB.%20As%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20almost%2050%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20chest%20problems%20did%20not%20go%20for%20a%20checkup%20until%20they%20started%20vomiting%20blood.%20And%20once%20they%20reached%20this%20stage%2C%20it%20was%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20too%20late.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20there%20were%20only%20three%20doctors%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20at%20that%20time%20and%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20help.%20They%20had%20heard%20about%20doctors%20in%20Kolkata%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259846%2Fdoctors-couple-covid-relief-free-medicine-collection-underprivileged-shell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20medicines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CSabitri%20and%20I%20started%20making%20trips%20to%20these%20clinics%20to%20collect%20the%20medicine%20samples%20which%20we%20distributed%20in%20a%20small%20room%20that%20a%20tea%20shop%20owner%20had%20lent%20to%20us.%20Through%20the%20w