0He%20adds%20that%20they%20procure%20these%20medicines%20from%20the%20Government%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20community%20delivery%20centres%20ensure%20that%20women%20have%20a%20safe%20environment%20where%20they%20can%20give%20birth%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fshis-1-1714725680-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348891%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20community%20delivery%20centres%20ensure%20that%20women%20have%20a%20safe%20environment%20where%20they%20can%20give%20birth%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20project%20is%20the%20community%20delivery%20centres%2C%20through%20which%20SHIS%20ensures%20that%20expectant%20mothers%20have%20a%20safe%2C%20compassionate%20and%20nurturing%20environment%20where%20they%20can%20deliver%20their%20babies.%20Currently%2C%20three%20community%20centres%20are%20operated%20at%20Bayermari%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Jumainaskar%20in%20Kakdwip%20Block%2C%20and%20Rakhalpur%20in%20Patharpratima%20Block.%20Each%20centre%20has%20all%20the%20necessary%20medical%20equipment%20for%20a%20smooth%20delivery%20and%20a%20stabilisation%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C