ckshaw%20pullers%20will%20get%20the%20funds%20to%20buy%20e-rickshaws%20which%20will%20help%20ease%20their%20task%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Sunil%20Shinde%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20how%20does%20this%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20an%20individual%20invests%20in%20a%20certain%20project%20on%20our%20platform%2C%20the%20money%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20investee%20via%20a%20regulated%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ram%20explains.%20He%20adds%20that%20Rang%20De%20is%20regulated%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20and%20has%20their%20NBFC-P2P%20(Non-Banking%20Financial%20Company)%20licence%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20allows%20any%20Indian%20to%20lend%20money%20to%20a%20fellow%20Indian%20over%20the%20internet%20through%20our%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20money%20is%20invested%2C%20a%20lot%20ensues%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20the%20funds%20to%20meet%20its%20purpose.%20In%20this%20particular%20project%2C%20Rang%20De%20has%20partnered%20with%20Tisser%20%E2%80%94%20a%20not-for-profit%20trust%20that%20is%20providing%20sustainable%20livelihoods%2C%20income%20opportunities%2C%20and%20access%20to%20professional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344574%2Ftata-samvaad-tribal-conclave-preserves-lost-heritage-artisans-sell-handicrafts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20craftspersons%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20through%20professional%20training%2C%20innovative%20models%2C%20and%20technological%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETisser%20identifies%20the%20rickshaw-pullers%20who%20wish%20to%20upgrade%20to%20e-rickshaws%2C%20helps%20them%20with%20finances%20(they%20have%20raised%20over%20Rs%2014%2C00%2C000)%20and%20ensures%20that%20these%20rickshaw-pullers%20repay%20the%20loan%20with%20interest%20every%20month%20over%2030%20months.%20Ram%20adds%20that%20another%20suppor