20across%20several%20states%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20temperatures%20have%20soared%20between%2040%20to%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20parts%20of%20Odisha%20earlier%20this%20week.%20Similar%20conditions%20have%20been%20observed%20in%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20and%20southwestern%20parts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20among%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERising%20temperatures%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20use%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20air%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20electricity%20as%20people%20try%20to%20escape%20the%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20from%20home%20becomes%20more%20challenging%20as%20the%20temperature%20starts%20to%20rise%20as%20early%20as%207%20am.%20Living%20in%20apartments%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20us%20much%20room%20to%20naturally%20cool%20the%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinaya%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20situation%20may%20seem%20bleak%2C%20architects%20and%20designers%20suggest%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20geography%2C%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20keep%20your%20home%20naturally%20cool.%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20with%20several%20experts%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20secrets%20of%20designing%20a%20%E2%80%98cool%E2%80%99%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20Back%20To%20Your%20Roots%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20look%20back%20at%20the%20houses%20that%20our%20ancestors%20built%2C%20the%20structures%20with%20open%20spaces%2C%20inward-looking%20homes%20with%20courtyards%20and%20huge%20windows%20helped%20to%20keep%20the%20home%20naturally%20cool.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamira%20Rathod%2C%20an%20archi