uld%20speak%20in%20Hindi.%20We%20speak%20Rajasthani%20and%20Haryanvi%20at%20home.%20It%20was%20only%20teachers%20who%20would%20speak%20in%20Hindi%20in%20our%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Bhavesh%20started%20recording%20videos%20when%20there%20was%20no%20one%20around.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20making%20videos%20on%20catchy%20topics%20like%20how%20many%20litres%20of%20cow%20milk%20is%20required%20to%20make%20one%20litre%20of%20pure%20ghee.%20I%20also%20learnt%20digital%20marketing%20to%20utilise%20it%20for%20boosting%20my%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20Bhavesh%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20in%20April%202021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20happy%20to%20get%20this%20boost%20%E2%80%93%20this%20was%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20what%20my%20friends%20in%20government%20jobs%20were%20earning.%20A%20month%20later%20in%20May%2C%20I%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%206%20lakh%20and%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%201.8%20lakh.%20I%20was%20so%20thrilled%20that%20I%20refreshed%20my%20account%20multiple%20times%20in%20the%20day%20to%20check%20the%20balance.%20It%20was%20a%20large%20amount%20for%20an%20unemployed%20person%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20year%2C%20he%20established%20a%20shed%20to%20increase%20the%20cattle%20at%20his%20home.%20From%203-4%20cows%20initially%2C%20Bhavesh%20today%20has%20at%20least%2020%20cows%20at%20his%20home%20and%20is%20associated%20with%20150%20local%20farmers%20to%20source%20ghee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20failed%20entrepreneur%2C%20Bhavesh%20today%20earns%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20in%20a%20month%20and%20has%20established%20a%20customer%20base%20of%2015%2C000%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20just%20because%20I%20denied%20preparing%20for%20the%20government%20jobs%2C%20I%20was%20told%20I%20was%20useless.%20I%20kept%20hustling%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years.%20My%20family%20believed%20in%20my%20dreams%20only%20when%20I%20started%20earning%20decent%20amounts.%20I%20am%20grateful%20that%20today%20I%20am%20able%20to%20earn%20even%20more%20than%20my%20friends%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Kasutam%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714112020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FKasutam-2-1713339469.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347476%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20time%20when%20his%20friends%20secured%20government%20jobs%2C%20Bhavesh%20Chaudhary%20had%20no%20direction%20in%20life.%20Today%20he%20has%20established%20a%20multi-crore%20brand%20called%20Kasutam%2C%20selling%20homemade%20A2%20bilona%20ghee.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A61%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347476%2Fkasutam-bilona-ghee-business-haryana-man-bhavesh-chaudhary-sells-a2-ghee-earns-lakhs-per-months%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Gardener%20Grows%20Mango%2C%20Chikoo%2C%20Orange%20%26amp%3B%2014%20Other%20Fruits%20In%20Crates%20On%20Her%20Terrace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJayanti%20Sahoo%E2%80%99s%20day%20starts%20with%20harvesting%20guavas%2C%20mulberries%2C%20chikoos%2C%20and%20pomegranates%20from%20her%20lush%20green%20rooftop%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20days%2C%20people%20put%20chemicals%20to%20artificially%20ripen%20fruits.%20Fruits%20are%20coated%20with%20wax%20and%20chemicals%20to%20make%20them%20glossy.%20We%20are%20blessed%20to%20eat%20fruits%20that%20are%20completely%20chemical-free%20and%20organically%20grown.%20Our%20fruits%20are%20comparatively%20sweeter%20than%20those%20available%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20as%20I%20prepare%20to%20ask%20Jayanti%20all%20about%20her%20journey%20that%20led%20to%20her%20turning%20her%20very%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20350%20sq%20ft%20terrace%2C%20along%20with%20her%20three-storey%20house%20covering%20a%20total%20area%20of%20around%201%2C500%20sq%20ft%2C%20is%20thriving%20with%20a%20diverse%20array%20of%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20vacant%20place%20left%20in%20my%20home%20where%20I%20could%20add%20more%20pots.%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20more%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayanti%2C%20now%2056%20years%20old%2C%20narrates%20that%20it%20was%20during%20her%20childhood%20she%20took%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20gardening.%20Growing%20up%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Odisha%2C%20a%20young%20Jayanti%20lived%20along%20with%20her%20six%20siblings%20and%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20lived%20in%20a%20small%20home.%20My%20father%20would%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278952%2Fkerala-gardener-grows-135-fruit-trees-in-plastic-drums-on-terrace-shares-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20backyard%20and%20we%20helped%20him%20in%20gardening.%20We%20would%20be%20very%20excited%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20the%20well%20and%20water%20all%20the%20plants%20together.%20He%20would%20teach%20us%20how%20to%20take%20care%20of%20plants.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20be%20in%20the%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20piqued%20her%20interest%20in%20gardening%20and%20her%20desire%20to%20create%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20her%20own.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20would%20not%20grow%20flowering%20plants.%20But%20I%20always%20desired%20to%20grow%20roses%20and%20%3Cem%3Erajanigandha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tuberose).%20So%2C%20when%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20set%20up%20a%20small%20garden%20of%20roses%20and%20other%20flowers.%20My%20father%20would%20bring%20guests%20to%20my%20garden%20and%20proudly%20say%20that%20this%20was%20his%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20garden%2C%